<DIV>You can use the macros for MOST of your keys.&nbsp; Then have 1 hotkey that you actually link directly to the Song list.</FONT></DIV>
<DIV></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>use that as your /stopsong.&nbsp; Just tap that 1 key right before your clicky item.&nbsp; This way you can reduce your buttons significantly without making a specific /stopsong key.</FONT></DIV>
