												<P>/stop</P>
<P>/cast 1</P>
<P>/pause 27</P>
<P>/stop</P>
<P>/cast 2</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>easy way to twist 2 songs with one keystoke.I used to use /pause 30 ,but I have found I can it down as low as 27 and still have the songs get off.</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>As far as having a 3rd party program to automatically activate that hotkey for me every&nbsp; 1.5 minutes or so,I think that would be a bit too much.Part of playing a class is actually having to play the class.</P>
